title: Volquez sharp as Royals beat Blue Jays 5-0 in ALCS opener
text:
> Top News Volquez sharp as Royals beat Blue Jays 5-0 in ALCS opener Toronto Blue Jays' Troy Tulowitzki, right, has words with home plate umpire Tony Randazzo after being called out on strikes during the sixth inning of Game 1 of baseball's American League Championship Series against the Kansas City Royals in Kansas City, Mo., Friday, Oct. 16, 2015. (Nathan Denette/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT
